# Mosquitto ACL for MWS Assessment 2
# Principle: sensor publishes only its own telemetry/alerts; operator reads only required monitoring topics.

user sensor01
topic write mws/water/quality/sensor01/telemetry
topic write mws/water/quality/sensor01/alerts

user operator01
topic read mws/water/quality/+/telemetry
topic read mws/water/quality/+/alerts

# Read-only lab test account. It is intentionally blocked from publishing.
user lab_test
topic read mws/water/quality/+/telemetry
